## Data Source Patterns

| Element | Selector |
|---------|----------|
| Add new data source button | `[data-testid='data-testid data-source-add-button']` |
| Data source name input | `[data-testid='data-testid Data source settings page name input field']` |
| Filter data sources | `[placeholder='Filter by name or type']` |
| Search connections | `[aria-label='Search connections by name']` |
| Connection tile | `a[href='/connections/datasources/[plugin-id]/']` |

